{"TopicId":214198,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[1.12.x] FRS (Funds, Rep, Science)","CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-02T14:21:43Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-02T14:21:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA small request from a forum user who needed something a bit bigger for his eyes:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EFunds, Rep, Science\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022VzluhyD.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002267.10\u0022 height=\u0022155\u0022 width=\u0022231\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/VzluhyD.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a simple little mod which simply shows the Funds, Reputation and Science in a small, resizable, positionable window\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt the top of the window, there are specialized controls:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nX - Close button\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nToggle Skin\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nChange Font Size\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis mod was made to show this information when the game window is scaled larger than what the game supports (on a 4K monitor).\u003Cbr\u003E\nThat can be done by editing the settings.cfg, and changing the UI_SCALE parameter.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003EDependencies\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/169509-141-toolbar-controller-for-modders/\u00